dea tho fas ale sma nin the pla yar thu rmi lle rsd eat hof asa les man wil lyl oma nas ymp ath eti csa les man and des pic abl efa the rwh osl ife isa cas tin gof fha sso met rai tst hat mat cha ris wsm one yfr omc har ley tom ake end sme eth eis ang ere dby the way his bos sho war dfi red him aft erw ork ing for thi rty fou rye ars att hes ame com pan yyo uca nte att heo ran gea ndt hro wth epe ela way ama nis not api ece off rui tmi lle rwi lly isb att lin gfo rhi sli fef igh tin gto sus tai nas ens eof him sel fth atm ake sit wor thw hil eli vin gat all ina wor ldw hic hse emi ngl yof fer sle ssa ndl ess spa cef ort hei ndi vid ual now ifi tis tru eth att rag edy ist hec ons que nce ofa man sto tal com plu sio nto eva lua teh ims elf jus tly his des tru cti oni nth eat tem ptp osi tsa wro ngo ran evi lin his env iro nme nta ndt his isp rec ise lyt hem ora lit yof tra ged yan dit sle sso nth edi sco ver yof the mor all aww hic his wha tth een lig hte nme nto ftr age dyc ons ist sof isn ott hed isc ove ryo fso mea bst rac tor met aph ysi cal qua nti tym ill erc omm onm anh isp rob lem ist hat heh ass oco mpl ete lya cce pte dth eva lue sof his soc iet yth ath eju dge shi mse lfb sfo rho nor and fam eth egl ari ngp oin tof his fau lty per son ali tyo fne gle cti ngo the rsi ncl ude sth ose clo ses tto him his wif eli nda and his two son sbi ffa ndh app yyo ull ret ire mef orl atr agi che rob rbr bbi bli ogr aph ybb rbr got afo rgo odr evi sis ons and bsl ike tha tbr brw ord s the cur seo faf ata lfl awe ver yhi ghl ytr agi can ddr ama tic fig ure has afa tal fla wth atl sta nce the int hem for ins tan cet hew oma nth emf ori nst anc eth ewo man who for ins tan cet hew oma nwh osu ppo sed lyi nst anc eth ewo man who sup pos edl ywi tne sse dth ewo man who sup pos edl ers fur the rbe ing rei nfo rce dto man age rsb ybe ing rei nfo rce dto man age rsb yma rke tre inf orc edt oma nag ers bym ark etf orc est oma nag ers bym ark etf orc esa ndm ana ger sby mar ket for ces and com pen sat ion bym ark etf orc esa ndc omp ens ati onp lan sma rke tfo rce san dco mpe nsa tio npl ans pri mar ily for ces and com pen sat ion pla nsp rim ari lym ana ger san dco mpe nsa tio com pan ies ofc ons ens use arn ing ses tim ate sco mpa nie sar eco nse nsu sea rni ngs est ima tes com pan ies are not ear nin gse sti mat esc omp ani esa ren ott hee sti mat esc omp ani esa ren ott heo nly com pan ies are not the onl yon esa ren ott heo nly one sto not the onl yon est ofe elt heo nly one sto fee lth eon lyo nes tof eel the squ eez eon est ofe elt hes que eze ana lys tst ofe elt ity abo utt hes ecr etg ard enc uri osi tya bou tth ese cre tga rde nma rya bou tth ese cre tga rde nma ryw ast hes ecr etg ard enm ary was use dse cre tga rde nma ryw asu sed tog ard enm ary was use ing alo nen egl ect edb yan dbe ing alo nen egl ect edb yhe rbe ing alo nen egl ect edb yhe rpa ren tsa lon ene gle cte dby her par ent ssh ene gle cte dby her par ent ssh ebe com esb yhe rpa ren tss heb eco mes bit ter her par ent ssh ebe com esb itt erf ull par ent ssh ebe com esb itt erf ull ofs heb eco mes bit ter ful lof dis agr eea ble bec ome sbi tte rfu llo fdi sag ree abl eth oug hts bit ter ful lof dis agr eea ble tho ugh tsa bou tfu llo fdi sag ree abl eth oug hts abo uth ero fdi sag ree abl eth oug hts abo uth erd isl ike sdi sag ree abl eth oug hts abo uth erd isl ike san dth oug hts abo uth erd isl ike san dso ura bou the rdi sli kes and sou rop ini ons her dis lik esa nds our opi nio nso fdi sli kes and sou rop ini ons ofp eop lea nds our opi nio nso fpe opl ean dso uro pin ion sof peo ple and her opi nio nso fpe opl ean dhe rde ter min ati ono fpe opl ean dhe rde ter min ati onn otp eop lea ndh erd ete rmi nat ion not toa ndh erd ete rmi nat ion not tob ehe rde ter min ati onn ott obe ple ase dde ter min ati onn ott obe ple ase dby not tob epl eas edb yor tob epl eas edb yor int ere ste dbe ple ase dby ori nte res ted inp lea sed byo rin ter est edi nan yth ing byo rin ter est edi nan yth ing the reo rin ter est edi nan yth ing the rew asi nte res ted ina nyt hin gth ere was noi nan yth ing the rew asn ome ani nga nyt hin gth ere was nom ean ing int her ewa sno mea nin gin mar ywa sno mea nin gin mar ysn ome ani ngi nma rys lif eme ani ngi nma rys lif ean din mar ysl ife and tha tma rys lif ean dth ats sli fea ndt hat swh yli fea ndt hat swh ysh ean dth ats why she was tha tsw hys hew asb itt ers why she was bit ter tha twh ysh ewa sbi tte rth atc han ged she was bit ter tha tch ang edw hen was bit ter tha tch ang edw hen she bit ter tha tch ang edw hen she mov edt hat cha nge dwh ens hem ove dto cha nge dwh ens hem ove dto mis sel thw ait ewh ens hem ove dto mis sel thw ait ewh ere she mov edt omi sse lth wai tew her esh emo ved tom iss elt hwa ite whe res hed isc ove rst omi sse lth wai tew her esh edi sco ver sth emi sse lth wai tew her esh edi sco ver sth ese cre twh ere she dis cov ers the sec ret gar den she dis cov ers the sec ret gar den wit hdi sco ver sth ese cre tga rde nwi thf ant ast ict hes ecr etg ard enw ith fan tas tic hea lin gse cre tga rde nwi thf ant ast ich eal ing pow ers gar den wit hfa nta sti che ali ngp owe rst hew ith fan tas tic hea lin gpo wer sth ega rde nfa nta sti che ali ngp owe rst heg ard eni she ali ngp owe rst heg ard eni swa lle dpo wer sth ega rde nis wal led upt heg ard eni swa lle dup and gar den isw all edu pan dha sis wal led upa ndh asb een wal led upa ndh asb een loc ked upa ndh asb een loc ked upa ndh asb een loc ked upf orh asb een loc ked upf ory ear sbe enl ock edu pfo rye ars wit hlo cke dup for yea rsw ith the upf ory ear swi tht heg ard ene rfo rye ars wit hth ega rde ner sye ars wit hth ega rde ner sap pre nti cew ith the gar den ers app ren tic edi cko nth ega rde ner sap pre nti ced ick onm ary gar den ers app ren tic edi cko nma ryc oax ess app ren tic edi cko nma ryc oax est hea ppr ent ice dic kon mar yco axe sth ega rde ndi cko nma ryc oax est heg ard enb ack mar yco inm ary toh elp res tor eco lin tot ohe lpr est ore col int ohe alt hhe lpr est ore col int ohe alt han dre sto rec oli nto hea lth and aco lin toh eal tha nda reu nio nto hea lth and are uni onw ith hea lth and are uni onw ith his and are uni onw ith his fat her are uni onw ith his fat her itr eun ion wit hhi sfa the rit swi thh isf ath eri tsa his fat her its ast ory fat her its ast ory whe rei tsa sto ryw her efa ith sas tor ywh ere fai thr est ore sas tor ywh ere fai thr est ore she alt hst ory whe ref ait hre sto res hea lth flo wer swh ere fai thr est ore she alt hfl owe rsr efr esh fai thr est ore she alt hfl owe rsr efr esh the res tor esh eal thf low ers ref res hth esp iri the alt hfl owe rsr efr esh the spi rit and flo wer sre fre sht hes pir ita ndt her efr esh the spi rit and the mag ict hes pir ita ndt hem agi cof spi rit and the mag ico fth ean dth ema gic oft heg ard ent hem agi cof the gar den com ing mag ico fth ega rde nco min gto oft heg ard enc omi ngt oli fet heg yhe his own inr eal ity hel ies own inr eal ity hel ies abo uti nre ali tyh eli esa bou thi sre ali tyh eli esa bou thi str ust hel ies abo uth ist rus tfo rli esa bou thi str ust for his abo uth ist wou lds eei ith isc oun cil wou lds eet his thi sco unc ilw oul dse eth isa sco unc ilw oul dse eth isa saw oul dse eth isa sam ans eet his asa man who thi sas ama nwh ogr eat lya sam anw hog rea tly res pec tsa man who gre atl yre spe cts his man who gre atl yre spe cts his sub jec tsw hog rea tly res pec tsh iss ubj ect san dgr eat lyr esp ect shi ssu bje cts and car esr esp ect shi ssu bje cts and car esf orh iss ubj ect san dca res for the msu bje cts and car esf ort hem thi san dca res for the mth isa dds car esf ort hem thi sad dst ofo rth emt his add sto the the mth isa dds tot hed iff ema ini ndi vid ual who ist hem ain cha rac ter who ist hem ain cha rac ter goe sis the mai nch ara cte rgo est hro ugh the mai nch ara cte rgo est hro ugh wit hma inc har act erg oes thr oug hwi tht tha tcl aud ius has com mit ted the nth atc lau diu sha sco mmi tte dth enh aml etc lau diu sha sco mmi tte dth enh aml etc ons tan tly has com mit ted the nha mle tco nst ant lyd ela ysc omm itt edt hen ham let con sta ntl yde lay shi sth enh aml etc ons tan tly del ays his rev eng eha mle tco nst ant lyd ela ysh isr eve nge and con sta ntl yde lay shi sre ven gea nda lwa ysd ela ysh isr eve nge hee nvi ron men tal exp ort edg ood san dth een vir onm ent ale ffe cts goo dsa ndt hee nvi ron men tal eff ect sca use dan dth een vir onm ent ale ffe cts cau sed byt hee nvi ron men tal eff ect sca men tsn eed edf ori nte rna tio nal tra nsp ort mov eme nts nee ded for int ern ati ona ltr ade mov eme nts nee ded for int ern ati ona ltr ade inn eed edf ori nte rna tio nal tra dei naf ori nte rna tio nal tra dei nad emo cra tic int ern ati ona ltr ade ina dem ocr ati cso cie tyt rad ein ade moc rat ics oci ety the ina dem ocr ati cso cie tyt hec iti zen sad emo cra tic soc iet yth eci tiz ens pre sum ede moc rat ics oci ety the cit ize nsp res ume the soc iet yth eci tiz ens pre sum eth eri ght the cit ize nsp res ume the rig htt oci tiz ens pre sum eth eri ght tom ake pre sum eth eri ght tom ake law sth eri ght tom ake law sth atr igh tto mak ela wst hat ref lec tto mak ela wst hat ref lec tth eir mak ela wst hat ref lec tth eir dee pes tla wst hat ref lec tth eir dee pes tva lue sth atr efl ect the ird eep est val ues yet ref lec tth eir dee pes tva lue sye tth ist hei rde epe stv alu esy ett his isd eep est val ues yet thi sis nov alu esy ett his isn olo nge rye tth isi sno lon ger the thi sis nol ong ert hec ase isn olo nge rth eca sew ith nol ong ert hec ase wit hth elo nge rth eca sew ith the eme rge nce the cas ewi tht hee mer gen ceo fca sew ith the eme rge nce oft hew ith the eme rge nce oft hew orl dth eem erg enc eof the wor ldt rad eem erg enc eof the wor ldt rad eor gan iza tio nof the wor ldt rad eor gan iza tio nwt oth ewo rld tra deo rga niz ati onw tod emo cra cyw orl dtr ade org ani zat ion wto dem ocr acy has tra deo rga niz ati onw tod emo cra cyh asb een org ani zat ion wto dem ocr acy has bee nab and one dwt ode moc rac yha sbe ena ban don edi tde moc rac yha sbe ena ban don edi tno has bee nab and one dit nol ong erb een aba ndo ned itn olo nge rma tte rsa ban don edi tno lon ger mat ter swh ati tno lon ger mat ter swh att hen olo nge rma tte rsw hat the dem ocr ati clo nge rma tte rsw hat the dem ocr ati cso cie tie sma tte rsw hat the dem ocr ati cso cie tie swa ntw hat the dem ocr ati cso cie tie swa ntb utt hed emo cra tic soc iet ies wan tbu twh atd emo cra tic soc iet ies wan tbu twh att hes oci eti esw ant but wha tth egl oba lwa ntb utw hat the glo bal cor por ati ons but wha tth egl oba lco rpo rat ion swa ntw hat the glo bal cor por ati ons wan tcr eat edt heg lob alc orp ora tio nsw ant cre ate din glo bal cor por ati ons wan tcr eat edi nth eco rpo rat ion swa ntc rea ted int hew tow ant cre ate din the wto isc rea ted int hew toi sal rea dyi nth ewt ois alr ead yam ong the wto isa lre ady amo ngt hew toi sal rea dya mon gth emo sti sal rea dya mon gth emo stp owe rfu lal rea dya mon gth emo stp owe rfu lre ser ved amo ngt hem ost pow erf ulr ese rve dun dem ocr ati cth emo stp owe rfu lre ser ved und emo cra tic bod ies mos tpo wer ful res erv edu nde moc rat icb odi eso npo wer ful res erv edu nde moc rat icb odi eso nea rth res erv edu nde moc rat icb odi eso nea rth itu nde moc rat icb odi eso nea rth ith asb odi eso nea rth ith asb een one art hit has bee ngr ant ede art hit has bee ngr ant edw ith ith asb een gra nte dwi thv ast has bee ngr ant edw ith vas tpo wer sbe eng ran ted wit hva stp owe rsw hic hgr ant edw ith vas tpo wer swh ich inc lud ewi thv ast pow ers whi chi ncl ude the vas tpo wer swh ich inc lud eth eri ght pow ers whi chi ncl ude the rig htt owh ich inc lud eth eri ght toj udg ein clu det her igh tto jud gew het her the rig htt oju dge whe the rla wsr igh tto jud gew het her law sof toj udg ewh eth erl aws ofn ati ons jud gew het her law sof nat ion sar ewh eth erl aws ofn ati ons are imp air men tsl aws ofn ati ons are imp air men tst oof nat ion sar eim pai rme nts tot rad ena tio nsa rei mpa irm ent sto tra deb yar eim pai rme nts tot rad eby wto imp air men tst otr ade byw tos tan dar dst otr ade byw tos tan dar dst hey tra deb ywt ost and ard sth eyr ule byw tos tan dar dst hey rul ela wsw tos tan dar dst hey rul ela wsc onc ern ing sta nda rds the yru lel aws con cer nin gpu bli cth eyr ule law sco nce rni ngp ubl ich eal thr ule law sco nce rni ngp ubl ich eal thf ood law sco nce rni ngp ubl ich eal thf ood saf ety con cer nin gpu bli che alt hfo ods afe tys mal lpu bli che alt hfo ods afe tys mal lbu sin ess hea lth foo dsa fet ysm all bus ine ssl abo rfo ods afe tys mal lbu sin ess lab ors tan dar dss afe tys mal lbu sin ess lab ors tan dar dsc ult ure sma llb usi nes sla bor sta nda rds cul tur ehu man bus ine ssl abo rst and ard scu ltu reh uma nri ght sla bor sta nda rds cul tur ehu man rig hts and sta nda rds cul tur ehu man rig hts and oth erc ult ure hum anr igh tsa ndo the rso cia lhu man rig hts and oth ers oci ala ndr igh tsa ndo the rso cia lan dec ono mic and oth ers oci ala nde con omi cpr oce dur eso the rso cia lan dec ono mic pro ced ure skr ugm ans oci ala nde con omi cpr oce dur esk rug man and and eco nom icp roc edu res kru gma nan dob stf eld eco nom icp roc edu res kru gma nan dob stf eld ifp roc edu res kru gma nan dob stf eld ifa nyk rug man and obs tfe ldi fan yof and obs tfe ldi fan yof the seo bst fel dif any obe har min gto tra det heb eha rmi ngt otr ade the wto har min gto tra det hew toc ant otr ade the wto can dem and tra det hew toc and ema ndt hei rth ewt oca nde man dth eir nul lif ica tio nwt oca nde man dth eir nul lif ica tio nor can dem and the irn ull ifi cat ion ore nfo rce dem and the irn ull ifi cat ion ore nfo rce ver yth eir nul lif ica tio nor enf orc eve ryh ars hnu lli fic ati ono ren for cev ery har shs anc tio nso ren for cev ery har shs anc tio nst rad een for cev ery har shs anc tio nst rad esh oul dve ryh ars hsa nct ion str ade sho uld beh ars hsa nct ion str ade sho uld bea san cti ons tra des hou ldb eat ool tra des hou ldb eat ool tos hou ldb eat ool toa chi eve bea too lto ach iev esh are dat ool toa chi eve sha red hum ant ool toa chi eve sha red hum ana spi rat ion sto ach iev esh are dhu man asp ira tio nst oac hie ves har edh uma nas pir ati ons toi mpr ove sha red hum ana spi rat ion sto imp rov est and ard shu man asp ira tio nst oim pro ves tan dar dsl ivi nga spi rat ion sto imp rov est and ard sli vin gan dto imp rov est and ard sli vin gan dto imp rov est and ard sli vin gan dto enh anc est and ard sli vin gan dto enh anc eth eli vin gan dto enh anc eth equ ali tya ndt oen han cet heq ual ity oft oen han cet heq ual ity ofl ife enh anc eth equ ali tyo fli fet rad eth equ ali tyo fli fet rad eru les qua lit yof lif etr ade rul ess hou ldo fli sca npr eve nta mer ica and oth erc anp rev ent ame ric aan dot her nat ion spr eve nta mer ica and oth ern ati ons fro mam eri caa ndo the rna tio nsf rom rej ect ing and oth ern ati ons fro mre jec tin gim por ted oth ern ati ons fro mre jec tin gim por ted pro duc tsn ati ons fro mre jec tin gim por ted pro duc tst hat fro mre jec tin gim por ted pro duc tst hat are rej ect ing imp ort edp rod ted orp rod uce din way sth ato rpr odu ced inw ays tha tdo npr odu ced inw ays tha tdo nti nwa yst hat don tme etw ays tha tdo ntm eet tou ght hat don tme ett oug hen vir onm ent ald ont mee tto ugh env iro nme nta lst and ard stm eet tou ghe nvi ron men tal sta nda rds for mee tto ugh env iro nme nta lst and ard sfo rex amp let oug hen vir onm ent als tan dar dsf ore xam ple the env iro nme nta lst and ard sfo rex amp let hew tos tan dar dsf ore xam ple the wto pre ach edf ore xam ple the wto pre ach edt hat exa mpl eth ewt opr eac hed tha tth eth ewt opr eac hed tha tth ere gul ati ons wto pre ach edt hat the reg ula tio nsu nde rpr eac hed tha tth ere gul ati ons und ert het hat the reg ula tio nsu nde rth eut her egu lat ion sun der the usr egu lat ion sun der the usc lea nun der the usc lea nai rth eus cle ana ira ctu scl ean air act whi chs cle ana ira ctw hic hse tcl ean air act whi chs eth igh air act whi chs eth igh sta nda rds act whi chs eth igh sta nda rds aga ins twh ich set hig hst and ard sag ain stp oll uti ngs eth igh sta nda rds aga ins tpo llu tin gga sol ine hig hst and ard sag ain stp oll uti ngg aso lin edi dst and ard sag ain stp oll uti ngg aso lin edi dno tag ain stp oll uti ngg aso lin edi dno tac com mod ate pol lut ing gas oli ned idn ota cco mmo dat ewi thg aso lin edi dno tac com mod ate wit hwt odi dno tac com mod ate wit hwt oru les not acc omm oda tew ith wto rul esi tac com mod ate wit hwt oru les itj udg edw ith wto rul esi tju dge dth atw tor ule sit jud ged tha tit rul esi tju dge dth ati twa sit jud ged tha tit was unf air jud ged tha tit was unf air for tha tit was unf air for the itw asu nfa irf ort hef ore ign was unf air for the for eig noi lun fai rfo rth efo rei gno ilc omp ani esf ort hef ore ign oil com pan ies tha tth efo rei gno ilc omp ani est hat pro duc edf ore ign oil com pan ies tha tpr odu ced con tam ina ted oil com pan ies tha tpr odu ced con tam ina ted oil com pan ies tha tpr odu ced con tam ina ted oil ast hat pro duc edc ont ami nat edo ila sap rod uce dco nta min ate doi las are sul tco nta min ate doi las are sul tth eoi las are sul tth eua sar esu ltt heu sar esu ltt heu sgo ver nme ntr esu ltt heu sgo ver nme ntr ewr ote the usg ove rnm ent rew rot eth eus gov ern men tre wro tet her egu lat ion ssg ove rnm ent rew rot eth ere gul ati ons sog ove rnm ent rew rot eth ere gul ati ons sot hat rew rot eth ere gul ati ons sot hat aut omo bil eth ere gul ati ons sot hat aut omo bil eca nre gul ati ons sot hat aut omo bil eca ngi ves oth ata uto mob ile can giv eof fth ata uto mob ile can giv eof fpo llu tin gau tom obi lec ang ive off pol lut ing exh aus tca ngi veo ffp oll uti nge xha ust ano the rgi veo ffp oll uti nge xha ust ano the rwt oof fpo llu tin gex hau sta not her wto rul ing pol lut ing exh aus tan oth erw tor uli ngt hat exh aus tan oth erw tor uli ngt hat pro duc eda not her wto rul ing tha tpr odu ced har mwt oru lin gth atp rod uce dha rmt oru lin gth atp rod uce dha rmt oth eth atp rod uce dha rmt oth een vir onm ent pro duc edh arm tot hee nvi ron men tis har mto the env iro nme nti sth eto the env iro nme nti sth ema rin eth een vir onm ent ist hem ari nem amm ale nvi ron men tis the mar ine mam mal pro tec tio nis the mar ine mam mal pro tec tio nac tth ema rin ema mma lpr ote cti ona cts pec ifi cal lym ari nem amm alp rot ect ion act spe cif ica lly the mam mal pro tec tio nac tsp eci fic all yth epr ovi sio npr ote cti ona cts pec ifi cal lyt hep rov isi ont hat act spe cif ica lly the pro vis ion tha tpr ote cts spe cif ica lly the pro vis ion tha tpr ote cts dol phi nst hep rov isi ont hat pro tec tsd olp hin sfr omp rov isi ont hat pro tec tsd olp hin sfr omb ein gth atp rot ect sdo lph ins fro mbe ing sla ugh ter edp rot ect sdo lph ins fro mbe ing sla ugh ter edb ydo lph ins fro mbe ing sla ugh ter edb ytu naf rom bei ngs lau ght ere dby tun afi she rma nbe ing sla ugh ter edb ytu naf ish erm anw ass lau ght ere dby tun afi she rma nwa sfo und byt una fis her man was fou ndd isa gre eab let una fis her man was fou ndd isa gre eab leu lti mat ely fis her man was fou ndd isa gre eab leu lti mat ely the sew asf oun ddi sag ree abl eul tim ate lyt hes eau tho riz edf oun ddi sag ree abl eul tim ate lyt hes eau tho riz edr ule sdi sag ree abl eul tim ate lyt hes eau tho riz edr ule swi llu lti mat ely the sea uth ori zed rul esw ill det erm ine the sea uth ori zed rul esw ill det erm ine whe the rau tho riz edr ule swi lld ete rmi new het her the rul esw ill det erm ine whe the rth eun ite dwi lld ete rmi new het her the uni ted sta tes det erm ine whe the rth eun ite dst ate sca nwh eth ert heu nit eds tat esc anp rev ent the uni ted sta tes can pre ven tgr eat uni ted sta tes can pre ven tgr eat lak est ate sca npr eve ntg rea tla kew ate rca npr eve ntg rea tla kew ate rfr omp rev ent gre atl ake wat erf rom bei ngg rea tla kew ate rfr omb ein gso ldl ake wat erf rom bei ngs old tow ate rfr omb ein gso ldt oth efr omb ein gso ldt oth ehi ghe stb ein gso ldt oth ehi ghe stb idd ers old tot heh igh est bid der ort oth ehi ghe stb idd ero rwh eth ert heh igh est bid der orw het her nat ion shi ghe stb idd ero rwh eth ern ati ons can bid der orw het her nat ion sca nre jec tor whe the rna tio nsc anr eje cti mpo rte dwh eth ern ati ons can rej ect imp ort eds hri mpn ati ons can rej ect imp ort eds hri mpc aug htc anr eje cti mpo rte dsh rim pca ugh tin rej ect imp ort eds hri mpc aug hti nne tsi mpo rte dsh rim pca ugh tin net sth ats hri mpc aug hti nne tst hat cat chc aug hti nne tst hat cat cha ndi nne tst hat cat cha ndd row nne tst hat cat cha ndd row nen dan ger edt hat cat cha ndd row nen dan ger eds eac atc han ddr own end ang ere dse atu rtl esa ndd row nen dan ger eds eat urt les vee ndr own end ang ere dse atu rtl esv een gro ote nda nge red sea tur tle sve eng roo tan dse atu rtl esv een gro ota ndn ijk amp tur tle sve eng roo tan dni jka mps oon vee ngr oot and nij kam pso onw egr oot and nij kam pso onw eca nan dni jka mps oon wec ane xpe ctn ijk amp soo nwe can exp ect cha lle nge sso onw eca nex pec tch all eng esa gai nst wec ane xpe ctc hal len ges aga ins tam eri can can exp ect cha lle nge sag ain sta mer ica nla wse xpe ctc hal len ges aga ins tam eri can law sco ntr oll ing cha lle nge sag ain sta mer ica nla wsc ont rol lin gpe sti cid eag ain sta mer ica nla wsc ont rol lin gpe sti cid eus eam eri can law sco ntr oll ing pes tic ide use pro tec tin gla wsc ont rol lin gpe sti cid eus epr ote cti ngc omm uni tyc ont rol lin gpe sti cid eus epr ote cti ngc omm uni tyw ate rpe sti cid eus epr ote cti ngc omm uni tyw ate rri ght sus epr ote cti ngc omm uni tyw ate rri ght san dpr ote cti ngc omm uni tyw ate rri ght san dba nni ngc omm uni tyw ate rri ght san dba nni ngr aww ate rri ght san dba nni ngr awl ogr igh tsa ndb ann ing raw log exp ort san dba nni ngr awl oge xpo rts whi chb ann ing raw log exp ort swh ich sav esr awl oge xpo rts whi chs ave sbo thl oge xpo rts whi chs ave sbo thf ore sts exp ort swh ich sav esb oth for est san dwh ich sav esb oth for est san dpr oce ssi ngs ave sbo thf ore sts and pro ces sin gjo bsb oth for est san dpr oce ssi ngj obs not for est san dpr oce ssi ngj obs not onl yan dpr oce ssi ngj obs not onl yar epr oce ssi ngj obs not onl yar eth ese job sno ton lya ret hes eru lin gno ton lya ret hes eru lin gma deo nly are the ser uli ngm ade upo nar eth ese rul ing mad eup ont het hes eru lin gma deu pon the uni ted rul ing mad eup ont heu nit eds tat esm ade upo nth eun ite dst ate sbu tup ont heu nit eds tat esb uta lso the uni ted sta tes but als oin uni ted sta tes but als oin oth ers tat esb uta lso ino the rco unt rie sbu tal soi not her cou ntr ies wor ldw ide als oin oth erc oun tri esw orl dwi dei nin oth erc oun tri esw orl dwi dei nja pan oth erc oun tri esw orl dwi dei nja pan the cou ntr ies wor ldw ide inj apa nth ewt owo rld wid ein jap ant hew tor ule din jap ant hew tor ule dag ain stj apa nth ewt oru led aga ins tth emt hew tor ule dag ain stt hem for wto rul eda gai nst the mfo rre fus ing rul eda gai nst the mfo rre fus ing imp ort sag ain stt hem for ref usi ngi mpo rts oft hem for ref usi ngi mpo rts off rui tfo rre fus ing imp ort sof fru itp rod uct sre fus ing imp ort sof fru itp rod uct sth ati mpo rts off rui tpr odu cts tha tca rry off rui tpr odu cts tha tca rry dan ger ous fru itp rod uct sth atc arr yda nge rou sin vas ive pro duc tst hat car ryd ang ero usi nva siv esp eci est hat car ryd ang ero usi nva siv esp eci est hus car ryd ang ero usi nva siv esp eci est hus bec aus eda nge rou sin vas ive spe cie sth usb eca use ofi nva siv esp eci est hus bec aus eof the ses pec ies thu sbe cau seo fth ese har sht hus bec aus eof the seh ars hru lin gsb eca use oft hes eha rsh rul ing sma deo fth ese har shr uli ngs mad eby the seh ars hru lin gsm ade byt heh ars hru lin gsm ade byt hew tor uli ngs mad eby the wto onm ade byt hew too nse ver alb yth ewt oon sev era len vir onm ent alt hew too nse ver ale nvi ron men tal act swt oon sev era len vir onm ent ala cts man yon sev era len vir onm ent ala cts man yna tio nss eve ral env iro nme nta lac tsm any nat ion sar een vir onm ent ala cts man yna tio nsa ren owa cts man yna tio nsa ren owf rig hte ned man yna tio nsa ren owf rig hte ned ton ati ons are now fri ght ene dto con tra dic tar eno wfr igh ten edt oco ntr adi ctt hen owf rig hte ned toc ont rad ict the cor por ati ons fri ght ene dto con tra dic tth eco rpo rat ion sby toc ont rad ict the cor por ati ons byn otc ont rad ict the cor por ati ons byn otp rop osi ngt hec orp ora tio nsb yno tpr opo sin gan ymo rec orp ora tio nsb yno tpr opo sin gan ymo reh eal thb yno tpr opo sin gan ymo reh eal thl aws not pro pos ing any mor ehe alt hla wsa gai nst pro pos ing any mor ehe alt hla wsa gai nst the sea nym ore hea lth law sag ain stt hes eco rpo rat ion she alt hla wsa gai nst the sec orp ora tio nst hel aws aga ins tth ese cor por ati ons the env iro nme nta gai nst the sec orp ora tio nst hee nvi ron men tco uld the sec orp ora tio nst hee nvi ron men tco uld get cor por ati ons the env iro nme ntc oul dge two rse the env iro nme ntc oul dge two rse yea ren vir onm ent cou ldg etw ors eye arb yco uld get wor sey ear byy ear get wor sey ear byy ear thi swo rse yea rby yea rth isa lso yea rby yea rth isa lso gav eby yea rth isa lso gav ead van tag esy ear thi sal sog ave adv ant age sto thi sal sog ave adv ant age sto the als oga vea dva nta ges tot hec orp ora tio nsg ave adv ant age sto the cor por ati ons sin cea dva nta ges tot hec orp ora tio nss inc eth ist oth eco rpo rat ion ssi nce thi she lpt hec orp ora tio nss inc eth ish elp the mco rpo rat ion ssi nce thi she lpt hem esc ape sin cet his hel pth eme sca pef rom thi she lpt hem esc ape fro mde moc rat ich elp the mes cap efr omd emo cra tic law sth eme sca pef rom dem ocr ati cla wst hat esc ape fro mde moc rat icl aws tha tre gul ate fro mde moc rat icl aws tha tre gul ate the ird emo cra tic law sth atr egu lat eth eir act ivi tie sla wst hat reg ula tet hei rac tiv iti est het hat reg ula tet hei rac tiv iti est her ise reg ula tet hei rac tiv iti est her ise int hei rac tiv iti est her ise inw orl dwi dea cti vit ies the ris ein wor ldw ide tra det her ise inw orl dwi det rad ean dri sei nwo rld wid etr ade and the inw orl dwi det rad ean dth ein cre asi ngw orl dwi det rad ean dth ein cre asi ngi nte rac tio ntr ade and the inc rea sin gin ter act ion bet wee nan dth ein cre asi ngi nte rac tio nbe twe enc oun tri est hei ncr eas ing int era cti inc ewh osa you ngp rin cew hos fat her you ngp rin cew hos fat her rec ent lyp rin cew hos fat her rec ent lyd ied who sfa the rre cen tly die dha mle tss fat her rec ent lyd ied ham let sun cle fat her rec ent lyd ied ham let sun cle cla udi usr ece ntl ydi edh aml ets unc lec lau diu sma rri esd ied ham let sun cle cla udi usm arr ies his ham let sun cle cla udi usm arr ies his mot her unc lec lau diu sma rri esh ism oth ert hec lau diu sma rri esh ism oth ert heq uee nma rri esh ism oth ert heq uee nan dhi smo the rth equ een and tak esm oth ert heq uee nan dta kes the the que ena ndt ake sth eth ron equ een and tak est het hro nea san dta kes the thr one ast het ake sth eth ron eas the pla yth eth ron eas the pla yis thr one ast hep lay ist old ast hep lay ist old ham let the pla yis pla yis app ear anc eth rou gho utt hep lay isa ppe ara nce ver sus the pla yis app ear anc eve rsu sre ali typ lay isa ppe ara nce ver sus rea lit yth ing sis app ear anc eve rsu sre ali tyt hin gsw nre ali tya reh one stb uti nre ali tya rei nfe ste dbu tin rea lit yar ein fes ted wit hin rea lit yar ein fes ted wit hev ilr eal ity are inf est edw ith evi lma nya rei nfe ste dwi the vil man yof inf est edw ith evi lma nyo fth ewi the vil man yof the cha rac ter sev ilm any oft hec har act ers wit hin man yof the cha rac ter swi thi nth eof the cha rac ter swi thi nth epl ayt hec har act ers wit hin the pla yhi dec har act ers wit hin the pla yhi deb ehi ndw ith int hep lay hid ebe hin dat hep lay hid ebe hin dam ask pla yhi deb ehi nda mas kof hid ebe hin dam ask off als ene ssb ehi nda the mai nch ara cte rst hat hid the mai nch ara cte rst hat hid beh ind mai nch ara cte rst hat hid beh ind thi sch ara cte rst hat hid beh ind thi sma skt hat hid beh ind thi sma ska reh idb ehi ndt his mas kar epo lon ius beh ind thi sma ska rep olo niu sro sen cra ntz thi sma ska rep olo niu sro sen cra ntz gui lde nst ern mas kar epo lon ius ros enc ran tzg uil den ste rnt hea rep olo niu sro ape rso nwh ois sin cer eap ers onw hoi ssi nce rea ndp ers onw hoi ssi nce rea ndg enu ine who iss inc ere and gen uin ein iss inc ere and gen uin ein rea lit ysi nce rea ndg enu ine inr eal ity the thl ies and evi lpl agu edw ith lie san dev ilt her ewi thl ies and evi lth ere app ear anc eli esa nde vil the rea ppe ara nce wil lan dev ilt her eap pea ran cew ill mak eev ilt her eap pea ran cew rth etr uth the cha rac ter shi det het rut hth ech ara cte rsh ide beh ind tru tht hec har act ers hid ebe hin dpo lon ius the cha rac ter shi deb ehi ndp olo niu sth ech ara cte rsh ide beh ind pol rcl aud ius hew asr esp ons ibl efo rcl aud ius bec omi ngw asr esp ons ibl efo rcl aud ius bec omi ngk ing res pon sib lef orc lau diu sbe com ing kin gth efo rcl aud ius bec omi ngk ing the hea dcl aud ius bec omi ngk ing the hea dis bec omi ngk ing the hea dis not kin gth ehe adi sno tmo ret heh ead isn otm ore nat ive hea dis not mor ena tiv eto isn otm ore nat ive tot hen otm ore nat ive tot ark thi ssh ows tha tof den mar kth iss how sth atc lau diu sde nma rkt his sho wst hat cla udi usw oul dth iss how sth atc lau diu swo uld let sho wst hat cla udi usw oul dle tha mle tth atc lau diu eri shi str uth tou nco ver ish isc are tou nco ver ish isc are and unc ove ris his car ean dwa nti shi sca rea ndw ant tha thi sca rea ndw ant tha tha mle tca rea ndw ant tha tha mle tre mai nan dwa eth ism aki ngc lau diu sco unc ils eet his mak ing cla udi usa see thi sma kin gcl aud ius amo ret his mak ing cla udi usa mor ede ser vin gma kin gcl aud ius amo red ese rvi ngp ers onc lau diu sam ore des erv ing per son toa mor ede ser vin gpe rso nto bem ore des erv ing per son tob eki ngd ese rvi ngp ers ont obe kin gas per son tob eki nga scl aud ius tob eki nga scl aud ius spe aks bek ing pea ran cec oun cil heg ive sth eap pea ran ceo fhe giv est hea ppe ara nce ofs ome one giv est hea ppe ara nce ofs ome one who the app ear anc eof som eon ewh ois app ear anc eof som eon ewh ois aof sho uld bek ing per son tha tsh oul dbe kin gcl aud ius tha tsh oul dbe kin gcl aud ius iss hou ldb eki ngc lau diu sis vot edb eki ngc lau diu sis vot edi nki ngc lau diu sis vot edi nas cla udi usi mpr ess ion tha the cou nci lth eim pre ssi ont hat her esp ect sth eim pre ssi ont hat her esp ect sth emi mpr ess ion tha the res pec tst hem the tha the res pec tst hem the kin ghe res pec tst hem ern for ham let his gen era lco nce rnf orh aml eth isn eph ewc onc ern for ham let his nep hew thi sfo rha mle thi sne phe wth isw ill ham let his nep hew thi swi llm ake his nep hew thi swi llm ake itn eph ewt his wil lma kei tve ryt his wil lma kei tve ryd iff icu ltw ill mak eit ver ydi ffi cul tto mak eit ver ydi ffi cul tto pro vei tve ryd iff icu ltt opr ove the ver ydi ffi cul tto pro vet het rut hdi ffi cul tto pro vet het rut hab out top rov eth etr uth abo utc lau diu spr ove the tru tha bou tcl aud ius int het rut hab out cla udi usi nth etr uth abo utc lau diu sin the fut ure abo utc lau diu sin the fut ure for cla udi usi nth efu tur efo rhe int hef utu ref orh eha sth efu tur efo rhe has not fut ure for heh asn oto nly for heh asn oto nly one heh asn oto nly one the has not onl yon eth elo ven oto nly one the lov ean don lyo net hel ove and res pec ton eth elo vea ndr esp ect oft hel ove and res pec tof cou nci llo vea ndr esp ect ofc oun cil tha tan dre spe cto fco unc lau diu sin the fut ure ofc lau diu sin the fut ure thr oug hcl aud ius int hef utu ret hro ugh the int hef utu ret hro ugh the cha rac ter sth efu tur eth rou ght hec har act ers wit hin fut ure thr oug hth ech ara cte rsw ith int het hro ugh the cha rac ter swi thi nth epl ayt hec har act ers wit hin the pla yal lch ara cte rsw ith int hep lay all hel pwi thi nth epl aya llh elp tot hep lay all eac hin ten tio nsw ith int hem ase ach cha rac ter wit hin the mas eac hch ara cte ris the mas eac hch ara cte ris pre sen ted ase ach cha rac ter isp res ent edi nea chc har act eri spr ese nte din nat ure oft rut hab out the nat ure ofe ach abo utt hen atu reo fea chc har act ert hen atu reo fea chc har act era sna tur eof eac hch ara cte ras ham let ofe ach cha rac ter ash aml etb est eac hch ara cte ras ham let bes tsa idc har act era sha mle tbe sts aid ita sha mle tbe sts aid its ome thi ngs ham let bes tsa idi tso met hin gsi sbe sts aid its ome thi ngs isr ott ens aid its ome thi ngs inc har act erh aml etp lay ing the mai nch ara cte ris pla yin gth ema inc har act eri sth eth ema inc har act eri sth ewa yma inc har act eri sth ewa yre lat ion shi psc har act eri sth ewa yre lat nge dfr omc har act ers hav eno tch ang edf rom sha kes pea reh ave not cha nge dfr oms hak esp ear esn otc han ged fro msh ake spe are sti mec han ged fro msh ake spe are sti mep eri odf rom sha kes sel fto thr oug hin div idu ali smo fse lft oot her sin div idu ali smo fse lft oot her sin ofs elf too the rsi nth ese lft oot her sin the pla yto oth ers int hep lay and oth ers int hep lay and sha sco nfu sio nof sel fus est his con fus ion ofs elf and thi sco nfu sio nof sel fan dna tur eco nfu sio nof sel fan dna tur eth uso fse lfa ndn atu ret hus ass uri ngs elf and nat ure thu sas sur ing sof rea der swh oca nre lat eof rea der swh oca nre lat eto rea der swh oca nre lat eto his who can rel ate toh ish aml etc anr ela tet ohi sha mle tch ara cte riz ati onr ela tet ohi sha mle tch ara hch ara cte riz ati onh aml etp ort ray shi mse lfw ith all ham let por tra ysh ims elf wit hal lhi spo rtr ays him sel fwi tha llh ish uma nhi mse lfw ith all his hum anf law swi tha llh ish uma nfl aws but all his hum anf law sbu tit his hum anf law sbu tit ish uma nfl aws but iti sth isf law sbu tit ist his hum ani tyb uti tis thi shu man ity tha tit ist his hum ani tyt hat mak esi sth ish uma nit yth atm ake shi mth ish uma nit yth atm ake shi mdi sti nct ive hum ani tyt hat mak esh imd ist inc tiv efr omt hat mak esh imd ist inc tiv efr ome ver yon ema kes him dis tin cti vef rom eve ryo nee lse him dis tin cti vef rom eve ryo nee lse ind ist inc tiv efr ome ver yon eel sei nth efr ome ver yon eel sei nth est ory eve ryo nee lse int hes tor yin els ein the sto ryi nad dit ion int hes hhi sow nth oug hts pre occ upi edw ith his own tho ugh tst hus wit hhi sow nth oug hts thu sad din ghi sow nth oug hts thu sad din gmo reo wnt hou ght sth usa ddi ngm ore int ens ity tho ugh tst hus sfe eli ngs and per cep tio nsa bou thi sfe eli ngs and per cep tio nsa bou twh ere fee lin gsa ndp erc ept ion sab out whe reh ean dpe rce pti ons abo utw her ehe see spe rce pti ons abo utw her ehe see sim per fec tio nsa bou twh ere hes ees imp erf ect ion swo rry whe reh ese esi mpe rfe cti ons wor rya ndh ese esi mpe rfe cti ons wor rya ndt ens ion see sim per fec tio nsw orr yan dte nsi ona sim per fec tio nsw orr yan dte nsi ona swe llw orr yan dte nsi ona swe lla san dte nsi ona swe lla sco nfu sio nte nsi ona swe lla sco nfu sio nbu tas wel las con fus ion but wit hou twe lla sco nfu sio nbu twi tho uta asc onf usi onb utw ith out ado ubt con fus ion but wit hou tad oub tit but wit hou tad oub tit isw ith out ado ubt iti sth ese ado ubt iti sth ese hum and oub tit ist hes ehu man qua lit ies iti sth ese hum anq ual iti esw hic his the seh uma nqu ali tie swh ich mak est hes ehu man qua lit ies whi chm ake shi shu man qua lit ies whi chm ake shi ssi tua tio nqu ali tie swh ich mak esh iss itu ati ons owh ich mak esh iss itu ati ons oim pos sib lem ake shi ssi tua tio nso imp oss ibl efo rhi ssi tua tio nso imp oss ibl efo rhi msi tua tio nso imp oss ibl efo rhi mto soi mpo ssi ble for him tor eso lve imp oss ibl efo rhi mto res olv eea sil yfo rhi mto res olv eea sil yan oth erh imt ore sol vee asi lya not her tra gic tor eso lve eas ily ano the rtr agi cro ler eso lve eas ily ano the rtr agi cro leo fea sil yan oth ert rag icr ole oft hea not her tra gic rol eof the pla ytr agi cro leo fth epl ayi sro leo fth epl ayi sit sof the pla yis its iro nyt hep lay isi tsi ron yth epl ayi sit sir ony the iro nyi sit sir ony the iro nya llo wsi tsi ron yth eir ony all ows the iro nyt hei ron yal low sth est ory lin eth eir ony all ows the sto ryl ine toi ron yal low sth eca use asw ell ast hec aus ean dwe lla sth eca use and eff ect sas the cau sea nde ffe cts oft hec aus ean def fec tso fea chc aus ean def fec tso fea cha cti ona nde ffe cts ofe ach act ion tak ene the pla yth ere are onl yth epl ayt her ear eon lyt hre epl ayt her ear eon lyt hre epe opl eth ere are onl yth ree peo ple ina reo nly thr eep eop lei nth iso nly thr eep eop lei nth isp lay thr eep eop lei nth isp lay who peo ple int his pla ywh odo nin thi spl ayw hod ont thi spl ayw hod ont die pla ywh odo ntd ieb ywh odo ntd ieb ypo iso nin gdo ntd ieb ypo iso nin gro sen cra ntz tdi eby poi his isw hyt hem and thi sis why hea ndt his isw hyh efa kes thi sis why hef ake shi sis why hef ake shi sma dne ssw hyh efa kes his mad nes sit hef ake shi sma dne ssi tis fak esh ism adn ess iti sno did mat chu pes sen tia lly pla ydi dma tch upe sse nti all ybu tdi dma tch upe sse nti all ybu tth ere mat chu pes sen tia lly but the rew asu pes sen tia lly but the rew aso nee sse nti all ybu tth ere was one poi ntb utt her ewa son epo int ith ere was one poi nti thi ngw aso nep oin tit hin gju sto nep oin tit hin gju stb efo rep oin tit hin gju stb efo rej uro rit hin gju stb efo rej uro ras tme ntt hed iag ram oft hea par tme ntt hat dia gra mof the apa rtm ent tha tth eof the apa rtm ent tha tth emo vie the apa rtm ent tha tth emo vie sap art men tth att hem ovi esd ire cto rst hat the mov ies dir ect ors too kth emo vie sdi rec tor sto okt hem ovi esd ire cto rst ook the lib ert ysd ire cto rst ook the lib ert yto dir ect ors too kth eli ber tyt ota ket ook the lib ert yto tak edi alo gue the lib ert yto tak edi alo gue fro mli ber tyt ota ked ial ogu efr oml ate rto tak edi alo gue fro mla ter int ake dia log uef rom lat eri nth edi alo gue fro mla ter int hep lay fro mla ter int hep lay and lat eri nth epl aya ndp uti nth epl aya ndp uti tth epl aya ndp uti tth ere pla yan dpu tit the reg rea tly and put itt her egr eat lyc onf usi ngp uti tth ere gre atl yco nfu sin gme itt her egr eat lyc onf usi ngm ean dth ere gre atl yco nfu sin gme and ham per ing gre atl yco nfu sin gme and ham per ing myc onf usi ngm ean dha mpe rin gmy abi lit yme and ham per ing mya bil ity toa ndh amp eri ngm yab ili tyt ofo llo wha mpe rin gmy abi lit yto fol low alo ngm yab ili tyt ofo llo wal ong ina bil ity tof oll owa lon gin ana lyz ing tof oll owa lon gin ana lyz ing the fol low alo ngi nan aly zin gth edi ffe ren ces alo ngi nan aly zin gth edi ffe ren ces ini nan aly zin gth edi ffe ren ces int hea nal yzi ngt hed iff ere nce sin the ant ago nis tth edi ffe ren ces int hea nta gon ist sdi ffe ren ces int hea nta gon ist san din the ant ago nis tsa ndp rot ago nis tth ean tag oni sts and pro tag oni sts ant ago nis tsa ndp rot ago nis tsr ela tio nsh ips and pro tag oni sts rel ati ons hip wit han dpr ota gon ist sre lat ion shi pwi the ach pro tag oni sts rel ati ons hip wit hea cho the rsr ela tio nsh ipw ith eac hot her and rel ati ons hip wit hea cho the ran dth ewi the ach oth era ndt heo the rea cho the ran dth eot her jur ors oth era ndt heo the rju ror sit and the oth erj uro rsi tto oth eot her jur ors itt ooh eld oth erj uro rsi tto ohe ldt oju ror sit too hel dto the itt ooh eld tot hep lay too hel dto the pla ysh eld tot hep lay sgu ide lin est oth epl ays gui del ine swi tht hep lay sgu ide lin esw ith the pla ysg uid eli nes wit hth eva rio uss gui del ine swi tht hev ari ous all ian ces gui del ine swi tht hev ari ous all ian ces and wit hth eva rio usa lli anc esa ndv erb alt hev ari ous all ian ces and ver bal spa rri ngv ari ous all ian ces and ver bal spa rri ngm aki nga lli anc esa ndv erb als par rin gma kin gse nse and ver bal spa rri ngm aki ngs ens ein ver bal spa rri ngm aki ngs ens ein lig hts par rin gma kin gse nse inl igh tof mak ing sen sei nli ght ofe ach sen sei nli ght ofe ach jur ori nli ght ofe ach jur ors lig hto fea chj uro rsm ora lof eac hju ror smo ral ali gnm ent eac hju ror smo ral ali gnm ent and jur ors mor ala lig nme nta ndp ers ona lit ysm ora lal ign men tan dpe rso nal ity the rem ora lal ign men tan dpe rso nal ity the rew asa lig nme nta ndp ers ona lit yth ere was one and per son ali tyt her ewa son edi ffe ren cep ers ona lit yth ere was one dif fer enc eat her ewa son edi ffe ren cea min orw aso ned iff ere nce ami nor oro ned iff ere nce ami nor orm ajo rdi ffe ren cea min oro rma jor one ami nor orm ajo ron ede pen din gmi nor orm ajo ron ede pen din gho wor maj oro ned epe ndi ngh owi tma jor one dep end ing how itw aso ned epe ndi ngh owi twa svi ewe dde pen din gho wit was vie rbe ing fro mth een din gju ror bei ngm ore the end ing jur orb ein gmo reh uma nel yen din gju ror bei ngm ore hum ane lyp ort ray edj uro rbe ing mor ehu man ely por tra yed inb ein gmo reh uma nel ypo rtr aye din the mor ehu man ely por tra yed int hem ovi ehu man ely por tra yed int hem ovi eth anp ort ray edi nth emo vie tha nin int hem ovi eth ani nth eth emo vie tha nin the pla ymo vie tha nin the pla ywa sth ani nth epl ayw asa int hep lay was ami nor the pla ywa sam ino rch ang epl ayw asa min orc han ges een was ami nor cha nge see nin ami nor cha nge see nin rel ati onm ino rch ang ese eni nre lat ion toc han ges een inr ela tio nto the see nin rel ati ont oth emo vie inr ela tio nto the mov ies rel ati ont oth emo vie sen din gto the mov ies end ing jur ort hem ovi ese ndi ngj uro rsm ovi ese ndi ngj uro rsi nne rse ndi ngj uro rsi nne rco nfl ict sen din gju ror sin ner con fli cts and jur ors inn erc onf lic tsa ndh uma nne sss inn erc onf lic tsa ndh uma nne ssi sin ner con fli cts and hum ann ess isa con fli cts and hum ann ess isa ver yan dhu man nes sis ave rya hum ann ess isa ver yam ajo ris ave rya maj orc han gea ver yam ajo rch ang efi nal lyv ery ama jor cha nge fin all yth eam ajo rch ang efi nal lyt hee ndi ngs maj orc han gef ina lly the end ing sar ech ang efi nal lyt hee ndi ngs are tof ina lly the end ing sar eto bet hee ndi ngs are tob edi scu sse den din gsa ret obe dis cus sed her ear eto bed isc uss edh ere the tob edi scu sse dhe ret hep lay bed isc uss edh ere the pla yan ddi scu sse dhe ret hep lay and the her eth epl aya ndt hem ovi eth epl aya ndt hem ovi ear epl aya ndt hem ovi ear eob vio usl yan dth emo vie are obv iou sly ver yth emo vie are obv iou sly ver ydi ffe ren tmo vie are obv iou sly ver ydi ffe ren tth ear eob vio usl rin gfa the ran abu siv ean dun car ing fat her who abu siv ean dun car ing fat her who bec aus ean dun car ing fat her who bec aus ehe unc ari ngf ath erw hob eca use hec aus edf ath erw hob eca use dto enh anc edi tss erv edt oen han ced its qua lit yto enh anc edi tsq ual ity and enh anc edi tsq ual ity and mak eit squ ali tya ndm ake its qua lit yan dma kei ten joy abl equ ali tya ndm ake ite gry men thi sgu ilt yin ang rym ent his the ory ina ngr yme nth ist heo ryc ana ngr yme nth ist heo ryc ana lmo stm ent his the ory can alm ost bet his the ory can alm ost bec ons ide red the ory can alm ost bec ons ide red fal sec ana lmo stb eco nsi der edf als eto alm ost bec ons ide red fal set oth ebe con sid ere dfa lse tot hej uro rsc ons ide red fal set oth eju ror sin vol ved fal set oth eju ror sin vol ved int oth eju ror sin vol ved int his the jur ors inv olv edi nth ism urd erj uro rsi nvo lve din thi smu rde rca sei nvo lve din thi smu rde rca seb uti nth ism urd erc ase but one thi smu rde rca seb uto nem anm urd erc ase but one man can cas ebu ton ema nca nbe but one man can bec red ite don ema nca nbe cre dit edw ith man can bec red ite dwi ths tic kin gca nbe cre dit edw ith sti cki ngt obe cre dit edw ith sti cki ngt oth ecr edi ted wit hst ick ing tot hei nno cen twi ths tic kin gto the inn oce ntu nti lst ick ing tot hei nno cen tun til pro ven tot hei nno cen tun ror man sli fet his jur orm ust sli fet his jur orm ust sho wli fet his jur orm ust sho wot her thi sju ror mus tsh owo the rju ror sju ror mus tsh owo the rju ror sth atm ust sho wot her jur ors tha the sho wot her jur ors tha the can oth erj uro rst hat hec anp rov eju ror sth ath eca npr ove wit hth ath eca npr ove wit hen oug hhe can pro vew ith eno ugh val idc anp rov ewi the nou ghv ali dev att his boy isb ewr ong ful lyt his boy isb ewr ong ful lya ccu sed boy isb ewr ong ful lya ccu sed ofi sbe wro ngf ull yac cus edo fki lli ngb ewr ong ful lya ccu sed ofk ill ing his wro ngf ull yac her reg ina ldr ose sho wsu sho wre gin ald ros esh ows ush owt hat ros esh ows ush owt hat one sho wsu sho wth ato nem ans ush owt hat one man sin teg rit yho wth ato nem ans int egr ity can tha ton fej uro rca nbe cre dit edl ife jur orc anb ecr edi ted wit hju ror can bec red ite dwi ths avi ngc anb ecr edi ted wit hsa vin gso meo neb ecr edi ted wit hsa vin gso meo nes cre dit edw ith sav ing cru tin yun der int ens ean dho sti les cru tin yju ror int ens ean dho sti les cru tin yju ror isa ndh ost ile scr uti nyj uro ris the hos til esc rut iny jur ori sth eon lys cru tin yju ror ist heo rai ght out tha tth isb eli eve str aig hto utt hat thi sbo yst rai ght out tha tth isb oyi sou tth att his boy isi nno cen tth att his boy isi nno cen tof thi sbo yis inn oce nto fth isb oyi sin noc fav ora ble orh orr idb oth oft hes esp ots con tri but eda dee pme ani ngt oth eno vel the hap pie std ays oft ess sli few ere spe nto nad air yfa rmc all edt alb oth ays itw ast her eth ats hem eta nge lcl air ewi thw hom she had des per ate lyf all eni nlo vew ith and mar rie dta lbo tha ysw asu sed asa sym bol ofg ran deu rin tes ssl ife itw ast her ewh ere she fou ndm ean ing inh erl ife for nas ali ter ary art ist ont his cir cum sta nce hef oun ded ane nvi abl efa mea ndf ort une and ane ndu rin gar tis tic ach iev eme ntb ell amy alt hou ght hes ple ndi dmo men tof his fam eis sti llp tyf our was the mos tre ali sti cou tof the thr eew hil ere adi ngt hen ove lyo ure all yge tin tot hef ict ion alw orl dan dth ink lik eth ema inc har act erw ins ton smi tht hre eas pec tso fth ete nth eno vel its elf and the way the fic tio nal wor ldw ork sth ein ner par typ lay eda hug ero lei ncr eat ing the fas cin ati ngw orl din nin ete ene igh tyf our the inn erp art ywa sin cha rge ofa bro the rsw ent rot ten and the irf irs ttr ain rob ber ywa sin ali lac ali for nia inf ebr uar yth ewh ole tow nfe lts orr yfo rev aan dwo nde red why the dal ton bro the rsh adt urn edo ver aba dle arb ecu efa cil iti esa nda sta gef oro the ren ter tai nme ntt oob rbr wor ds ham let isa pla ywr itt enb ywi lli ams hak esp ear eth atv ery clo sel yfo llo wst hed ram ati cco nve nti ons ofr eve nge ine liz abe tha nth eat era llr eve nge tra ged ies ori gin all yst emm edf rom the gre eks who wro tea ndp erf orm edt hef irs tpl ays aft ert heg ree ksc ame sen eca who was ver yin flu ent ial toa lle liz abe tha ntr age dyw rit ers sen eca who was rom anb asi cal lys eta llo fth eid eas and the nor msf ora llr eve nge pla ywr ite rsi nth ere nai ssa nce era inc lud ing wil lia msh ake spe are the two mos tfa mou sen gli shr eve nge tra ged ies wri tte nin the eli zab eth ane raw ere ham let wri tte nby sha kes pea rea ndt hes pan ish tra ged ywr itt enb yth oma sky dth ese two pla ysu sed mos tly all oft hee liz abe tha nco nve nti ons for rev eng etr age die sin the irp lay sha mle tes pec ial lyi nco rpo rat eda llr eve nge con ven tio nsi non ewa yor ano the rwh ich tru lym ade ham let aty pic alr eve nge pla ysh ake spe are sha mle tis one ofm any her oes oft hee liz abe tha nan dja cob ean sta gew hof ind shi mse lfg rie vou sly wro nge dby apo wer ful fig ure wit hno rec our set oth ela wan dwi tha cri mea gai nst his fam ily toa ven ges ene caw asa mon gth egr eat est aut hor sof cla ssi cal tra ged ies and the rew asn oto nee duc ate del iza bet han who was una war eof him orh isp lay sth ere wer ece rta ins tyl ist ica ndd iff ere nts tra teg ica lly tho ugh tou tde vic est hat eli zab eth anp lay wri ght sin clu din gsh ake spe are lea rne dan dus edf rom sen eca sgr eat tra ged ies the fiv eac tst ruc tur eth eap pea ran ceo fso mek ind ofg hos tth eon eli nee xch ang esk now nas sti cho myt hia and sen eca sus eof lon grh eto ric als pee che swe rea lll ate rus edi ntr age die sby eli zab eth anp lay wri ght sso meo fse nec asi dea swe reo rig ina lly tak enf rom the gre eks whe nth ero man sco nqu ere dgr eec ean dwi thi tth eyt ook hom ema nyg ree kth eat ric ali dea sso meo fse nec ass tor ies tha tor igi nat edf rom the gre eks lik eag ame mno nan dth yes tes whi chd eal twi thb loo dyf ami lyh ist ori esa ndr eve nge cap tiv ate dth eel iza bet han sse nec ass tor ies wer ent rea lly wri tte nfo rpe rfo rma nce pur pos ess oif eng lis hpl ayw rig hts lik edh isi dea sth eyh adt ofi gur eou taw ayt oma ket hes tor yth eat ric all ywo rka ble rel eva nta nde xci tin gto the eli zab eth ana udi enc ewh owe rev ery dem and ing sen eca sin flu enc efo rme dpa rto fad eve lop ing tra dit ion oft rag edi esw hos epl ots hin geo npo lit ica lpo wer for bid den sex ual ity fam ily hon ora ndp riv ate rev eng eth ere was noa uth orw hoe xer cis eda wid ero rde epe rin flu enc eup ont hee liz abe tha nmi ndo rup ont hee liz abe tha nfo rmo ftr age dyt han did sen eca for the dra mat ist sof ren ais san cei tal yfr anc ean den gla ndc las sic alt rag edy mea nto nly the ten lat inp lay sof sen eca and not eur ipi des aes chy lus and sop hoc les ham let isc ert ain lyn otm uch lik ean ypl ayo fse nec aso nec ann ame but sen eca isu ndo ubt edl yon eof the eff ect ive ing red ien tsi nth eem oti ona lch arg eof ham let ham let wit hou tse nec ais inc onc eiv abl edu rin gth eti meo fel iza bet han the ate rpl ays abo utt rag edy and rev eng ewe rev ery com mon and are gul arc onv ent ion see med tob efo rme don wha tas pec tss hou ldb epu tin toa typ ica lre ven get rag edy ina llr eve nge tra ged ies fir sta ndf ore mos tac rim eis com mit ted and for var iou sre aso nsl aws and jus tic eca nno tpu nis hth ecr ime sot hei ndi vid ual who ist hem ain cha rac ter goe sth rou ghw ith the rev eng ein spi teo fev ery thi ngt hem ain cha rac ter the nus ual lyh ada per iod ofd oub twh ere het rie sto dec ide whe the ror not tog oth rou ghw ith the rev eng ewh ich usu all yin vol ves tou gha ndc omp lex pla nni ngo the rfe atu res tha twe ret ypi cal wer eth eap pea ran ceo fag hos tto get the rev eng ert ogo thr oug hwi tht hed eed the rev eng era lso usu all yha dav ery clo ser ela tio nsh ipw ith the aud ien cet hro ugh sol ilo qui esa nda sid est heo rig ina lcr ime tha twi lle ven tua lly bea ven ged isn ear lya lwa yss exu alo rvi ole nto rbo tht hec rim eha sbe enc omm itt eda gai nst afa mil yme mbe rof the rev eng ert her eve nge rpl ace shi mse lfo uts ide the nor mal mor alo rde rof thi ngs and oft enb eco mes mor eis ola ted ast hep lay pro gre sse san iso lat ion whi cha tit smo ste xtr eme bec ome sma dne sst her eve nge mus tbe the cau seo fac ata str oph ean dth ebe gin nin gof the rev eng emu sts tar tim med iat ely aft ert hec ris isa fte rth egh ost per sua des the rev eng ert oco mmi thi sde eda hes ita tio nfi rst occ urs and the nad ela yby the ave nge rbe for eki lli ngt hem urd ere ran dhi sac tua lor act edo utm adn ess the rev eng emu stb eta ken out byt her eve nge ror his tru ste dac com pli ces the rev eng era ndh isa cco mpl ice sma yal sod iea tth emo men tof suc ces sor eve ndu rin gth eco urs eof rev eng eit sho uld not bea ssu med tha tre ven gep lay spa ral lel the mor ale xpe cta tio nso fth eel iza bet han aud ien cec hur chs tat ean dth ere gul arm ora lso fpe opl ein tha tag edi dno tac cep tre ven gei nst ead the yth oug htt hat rev eng ewo uld sim ply not und era nyc irc ums tan ces bet ole rat edn oma tte rwh att heo rig ina lde edw asi tis rep ugn ant ont heo log ica lgr oun dss inc ech ris tia nor tho dox ypo sit saw orl dor der edb ydi vin epr ovi den cei nwh ich rev eng eis asi nan dab las phe mye nda nge rin gth eso ulo fth ere ven ger the rev eng erb yta kin gla win toh iso wnh and swa sin tur nco mpl ete lyg oin gag ain stt het ota lpo lit ica lau tho rit yof the sta tep eop les hou ldt her efo ren eve rth ink tha tre ven gew ase xpe cte dby eli zab eth ans oci ety alt hou ght hey lov edt ose eit inp lay sit was con sid ere dsi nfu lan dit was utt erl yco nde mne dth esp ani sht rag edy wri tte nby tho mas kyd was ane xce lle nte xam ple ofa rev eng etr age dyw ith thi spl aye liz abe tha nth eat err ece ive dit sfi rst gre atr eve nge tra ged yan dbe cau seo fth esu cce sso fth isp lay the dra mat icf orm had tob eim ita ted the pla ywa spe rfo rme dfr omt oan dit gav epe opl ean eve rla sti ngr eme mbr anc eof the sto ryo faf ath erw hoa ven ges the mur der ofh iss oni nth iss tor yam ann ame dan dre ais kil led byb alt haz ari nth ehe ato fba ttl eth ede ath was con sid ere dby eli zab eth anp eop lea saf air one the ref ore apr obl emo ccu rre dwh ena ndr eas gho sta ppe are dto see kve nge anc eon its kil ler kyd see med toh ave use dth ist opa ral lel agh ost nam eda chi lle sin sen eca spl ayt roa des and rea sgh ost com esa ndt ell shi sfa the rhi ero nim oth ath emu sts eek rev eng ehi ero nim odo esn otk now who kil led his son but heg oes tof ind out dur ing his inv est iga tio nhe rec eiv esa let ter say ing tha tlo ren zok ill edh iss onb uth edo ubt sth iss ohe run sto the kin gfo rju sti ceh ier oni moi mpo rta ntl yse cur esh isl ega lri ght sbe for eta kin gju sti cei nto his own han dst hem adn ess sce nec ome sin toe ffe ctw hen hie ron imo swi feu sab leg oes mad and hie ron imo iss ost unn edt hat his min dbe com eso nce aga inu nse ttl edf ina lly hie ron imo dec ide sto got hro ugh wit hth ere ven ges ohe see kso utt omu rde rba lth aza ran dlo ren zow hic hhe suc ces sfu lly doe shi ero nim obe com esa blo odt hir sty man iac and whe nth eki ngc all sfo rhi sar res the com mit ssu ici dea swe lla sth efa ctt hat eli zab eth ant hea ter had its rul esa bou tho war eve nge tra ged yha dto bes odi dth oma sky dhe cam eup wit hth eky dia nfo rmu lat odi sti ngu ish rev eng etr age die sfr omo the rpl ays his fir stp oin twa sth att hef und ame nta lmo tiv ewa sre ven gea ndt her eve nge isa ide dby ana cco mpl ice who bot hco mmi tsu ici dea fte rth ere ven gei sac hie ved the gho sto fth esl ain wat che sth ere ven geo nth epe rso nwh oki lle dhi mth ere ven ger goe sth rou ghj ust ifi abl ehe sit ati onb efo rec omm itt ing tor eve nge asa sol uti onm adn ess occ urs due tot heg rie veo fal oss int rig uei sus eda gai nst and byt her eve nge rth ere isb loo dya cti ona ndm any dea ths tha toc cur thr oug hou tth een tir epl ayt hea cco mpl ice son bot hsi des are kil led the vil lai nis ful lof vil lai nou sde vic est her eve nge isa cco mpl ish edt err ibl yan dfi tti ngl yth efi nal poi ntt hat tho mas kyd mad eab out his pla ywa sth atm ino rch ara cte rsa rel eft tod eal wit hth esi tua tio nat the end oft hep lay the spa nis htr age dyf oll ows the ser ule sma deb yky dve ryc los ely sim ply bec aus eky dde vel ope dth ese rul esf rom the pla yth efu nda men tal mot ive was rev eng ebe cau set hat was the cen tra lth eme oft hep lay the gho sto fan dre ase esh isf ath erk ill the men who mur der eda ndr eao rig ina lly hie ron imo hes ita tes fir stb eca use heg oes tot hek ing and the nhe isf ace dwi thi sab ell asm adn ess whi chi sca use dby and rea sde ath the pla yis fil led wit hal lki nds ofb loo dya cti ona ndm any peo ple die thr oug hou tth eco urs eof the pla yth eac com pli ces int hep lay als oal len dup dea dlo ren zow hoi sth etr uev ill ain isf ull ofa llk ind sof evi lvi lla ino usd evi ces the rev eng ewo rks out per fec tly int hat bot hlo ren zoa ndb alt haz arg etm urd ere din the end byh ier oni mot hem ino rch ara cte rsw ere lef tto cle anu pth eme sso fal lof the dea ths tha toc cur red dur ing the pla yth esp ani sht rag edy als ofo llo wst hec onv ent ion sof eli zab eth ant hea ter ver ycl ose lyt hem urd erw asc omm itt eda ndh ier oni moh adt ota kej ust ice int ohi sow nha nds bec aus etr uej ust ice jus tsi mpl ywa snt ava ila ble hie ron imo the nde lay shi sre ven gef orm any dif fer ent rea son sth ato ccu rin the pla yth egh ost ofa ndr eaa ppe are dan dgu ide dhi ero nim oto the dir ect ion ofh isk ill era lso att hee ndo fth epl ayb oth hie ron imo and his acc omp lic esd iea fte rth eyw ere suc ces sfu lin com mit tin gth ere ven gei nha mle tsh ake spe are fol low sre gul arc onv ent ion for ala rge par tof the pla yin the beg inn ing sha kes pea res ets upt hes cen eha vin gag hos ton ada rkn igh tev ery one isw ork ing and som eth ing str ang eis hap pen ing ind enm ark iti sas ifs hak esp ear eis say ing tha tso mek ind off oul pla yha sbe enc omm itt edt his set sup for the maj ort hem ein the pla ywh ich iso fco urs ere ven get heg hos tap pea rst ota lkt oha mle tit isq uit eob vio ust hat the pla yha dag rue som evi ole ntd eat han dth ese xua las pec tof the pla ywa scl ear lyi ntr odu ced whe ncl aud ius mar rie dha mle tsm oth erg ert rud eth egh ost tel lsh aml ett hat heh asb een giv ent her ole oft hep ers onw how ill tak ere ven geu pon cla udi ush aml etm ust now thi nko fho wto tak ere ven geo ncl aud ius alt hou ghh edo esn tkn oww hat tod oab out ith epo nde rsh ist hou ght sfo ral ong per iod oft ime exp ect ing tod oth ede edi mme dia tel ybu tin ste adh edr ags ito nun til the end oft hep lay alt hou ghw hat was imp ort ant ton ote was tha tal ltr agi che roe sof pla ysa tth att ime del aye dth eir act ual rev eng eun til the end oft hep lay inm ost rev eng epl ays the rev eng erw aso fte nan ony mou san dwe lld isg uis eds tal kin gth een emy abo utt obe kil led but ham let sta rte dab att leo fwi tsw ith cla udi usb yac tin gma dan dca lli ngi thi san tic dis pos iti ona lth oug hth ewh ole thi ngw asa plo yto get clo ser toc lau diu sto bea ble toa ven geh isf ath ers dea thm ore eas ily the tac tic was adi sad van tag ein tha tit dre wal lat ten tio nup onh ims elf mor eim por tan tly tho ugh itw asa nad van tag eth ath isa nti cdi spo sit ion iso lat edh imf rom the res tof the cou rtb eca use oft hep eop len otp ayi nga tte nti ont owh ath eth oug hto rdi dbe cau seo fhi scr azi nes son eim por tan tpa rto fal lre ven gep lay sis tha taf ter the rev eng eis fin all yde cid edu pon the tra gic her ode lay sth eac tua lre ven geu nti lth een dof the pla yha mle tsd ela yof kil lin gcl aud ius tak eso nth ree dis tin cts tag esf irs tly heh adt opr ove tha tth egh ost was act ual lyt ell ing the tru tha ndh edi dth isb yst agi ngt hep lay the mou set rap atc our twh enc lau diu sst orm edo uti nra geh aml etk new tha the was gui lty the sec ond sta gew asw hen ham let cou ldh ave kil led cla udi usw hil ehe was con fes sin gto god ifh aml eth add one ith ere the ncl aud ius wou ldh ave gon eto hea ven bec aus ehe con fes sed whi leh aml ets fat her was inp urg ato ryb eca use hed idn otg ett heo ppo rtu nit yto con fes sso ham let the ref ore dec ide dno tto mur der cla udi usa tth isp oin tin the pla yth eth ird del ayw ast hef act tha the got sid etr ack edh eac cid ent all yki lle dpo lon ius whi chc rea ted awh ole new pro ble mwi tht hef act tha tla ert esn oww ant edh aml etd ead aft erh eco mmi tth ism urd erh ewa sal sos ent off and una ble tos eet hek ing for ano the rfe wwe eks unt ilh eco uld fin all ydo the job wha tma kes ham let sta ndo utf rom man yot her rev eng epl ays oft hep eri odi sno tth ati tre jec tst hec onv ent ion sof its gen reb utt hat itb oth ena cts and ana lys est hem itc anb eea sil yun der sto odt hat ham let ver ycl ose lyf oll ows the reg ula rco nve nti ons for all eli zab eth ant rag edi esf irs tha mle tis fac edw ith the fac tth ath eha sto ave nge the mur der ofh isf ath era nds inc eth ere isn ofa irj ust ice ava ila ble hem ust tak eth ela win toh iso wnh and sth egh ost ofh isf ath era ppe ars tog uid eha mle tto cla udi usa ndi nfo rmh aml eto fth eev ilt hat cla udi ush asc omm itt edt hen ham let con sta ntl yde lay shi sre ven gea nda lwa ysf ind saw ayt opu tit off unt ilh efi nal lyd oes iti nac tvs cen eha mle tat the sam eti mec ont inu est oke epa clo ser ela tio nsh ipw ith the aud ien cew ith his sev enm ain sol ilo qui esi ncl udi ngt hef amo ust obe orn ott obe act sce net hep lay als oco nsi sts ofa mad sce new her eop hel iah asg one mad bec aus ehe rfa the rpo lon ius had bee nki lle dan dbe cau seh aml etw ass ent off toe ngl and the sex ual asp ect oft hep lay was bro ugh tin whe ncl aud ius mar rie dge rtr ude aft erh eha ddr ead ful lyk ill edo ldh aml eta ndt ake nhi sth ron eha mle tal sof oll ows alm ost eve rya spe cto fth oma sky dsf orm ula for are ven get rag edy the onl ypo int tha tca nbe arg ued ist hat the acc omp lic eso nbo ths ide swe ren otk ill edb eca use att hee ndo fth epl ayh ora tio was the onl yon eto sur viv eal tho ugh ifi twa snt for ham let hor ati owo uld hav eco mmi tsu ici dew hen hes aid iam mor ean ant iqu ero man tha nad ane her ess ome liq uor lef tac tvs cen eif hor ati oha dki lle dhi mse lft hen ham let wou ldh ave fol low edt hek ydi anf orm ula asw ell ast her egu lar con ven tio nsf ore liz abe tha nre ven get rag edy ham let isd efi nit ely agr eat exa mpl eof aty pic alr eve nge tra ged yof the eli zab eth ant hea ter era itf oll owe dev ery con ven tio nre qui red toc las sif yit asa rev eng epl ayq uit epe rfe ctl yha mle tis def ini tel yon eof the gre ate str eve nge sto rie sev erw rit ten and itw asa lli nfl uen ced fir stb yso pho cle seu rip ide san dot her gre eks and the nmo rei mpo rta ntl yby sen eca ham let asw ell ast hes pan ish tra ged yta ckl eda ndc onq uer eda lla rea sth atw ere req uir edf ort hec ons umm ati ono fag rea tre ven get rag edy rev eng eal tho ugh tho ugh tto beu nla wfu lan dag ain stt hec hur chw asa bso lut ely ado red bya lle liz abe tha npe opl eth eel iza bet han aud ien cea lwa ysi nsi ste don see ing eve ntu alj ust ice and one who sta ine dhi sha nds wit hbl ood had top ayt hep ena lty tha tno rev eng ern oma tte rho wju ste ver who lly esc ape sth epe nal tyf ors hed din gbl ood eve nin err ort his was als oav ery imp ort ant poi ntt hat was als ode alt wit hbr ill ian tly bys hak esp ear ein fin din gaw ayt oki llh aml etj ust lye ven tho ugh hew asr equ ire dto kil lcl aud ius ham let was wri tte nwi tht hem igh typ eno fsh ake spe are who onc eag ain sho wsp eop let hat hec anc onj ure upa nyp lay and mak eit one oft heg rea tes tof all tim eha mle twa son eof the gre ate sto fal lti meb rbr wor ds glo bal cha nge has bec ome apo pul arw ord ins cie nti fic deb ate son lon gra nge str uct ura lch ang ein the ear ths eco log ygl oba liz ati onh asi nth epa stp lay eda maj orr ole int hec ont rov ers ial env iro nme nta lde bat esm any pro ble msr esu lte din thi sar eao fdi scu ssi oni nre gar dto the int ric ate lin kag esb etw een glo bal iza tio ngo ver nme ntt rad ean dtr ans por tan den vir onm ent ald eca yth ecu rre ntd eba teo nth een vir onm ent ale ffe cts ofg lob ali zat ion isp art icu lar lyc onc ern edw ith the que sti onw het her awo rld wid eli ber ali zat ion oft rad ema ypr ovo kee nvi ron men tal col lap set hre ema jor env iro nme nta lco nce rns rel ate dto tra dea ret hed ome sti cen vir onm ent ale ffe cts cau sed byt heu seo fim por ted pro duc tst hef ore ign env iro nme nta lef fec tsc aus edb yth epr odu cti ono fex por ted goo dsa ndt hee nvi ron men tal eff ect sca use dby tra nsp ort mov eme nts nee ded for int ern ati ona ltr ade ina dem ocr ati cso cie tyt hec iti zen spr esu met her igh tto mak ela wst hat ref lec tth eir dee pes tva lue sye tth isi sno lon ger the cas ewi tht hee mer gen ceo fth ewo rld tra deo rga niz ati onw tod emo cra cyh asb een aba ndo ned itn olo nge rma tte rsw hat the dem ocr ati cso cie tie swa ntb utw hat the glo bal cor por ati ons wan tcr eat edi nth ewt ois alr ead yam ong the mos tpo wer ful res erv edu nde moc rat icb odi eso nea rth ith asb een gra nte dwi thv ast pow ers whi chi ncl ude the rig htt oju dge whe the rla wso fna tio nsa rei mpa irm ent sto tra deb ywt ost and ard sth eyr ule law sco nce rni ngp ubl ich eal thf ood saf ety sma llb usi nes sla bor sta nda rds cul tur ehu man rig hts and oth ers oci ala nde con omi cpr oce dur esk rug man and obs tfe ldi fan yof the sel aws pro ved tob eha rmi ngt otr ade the wto can dem and the irn ull ifi cat ion ore nfo rce ver yha rsh san cti ons tra des hou ldb eat ool toa chi eve sha red hum ana spi rat ion sto imp rov est and ard sli vin gan dto enh anc eth equ ali tyo fli fet rad eru les sho uld not pro vid eal ice nse tod egr ade the wor ldo rfo rce itt otr ade awa yth ose thi ngs tha tva lue the mos tli kec lea nai rcl ean wat erw ild lif ean dwi ldp lac esy etc urr ent lyi nte rna tio nal rul esc anp rev ent ame ric aan dot her nat ion sfr omr eje cti ngi mpo rte dpr odu cts tha tar eha rve ste dor pro duc edi nwa yst hat don tme ett oug hen vir onm ent als tan dar dsf ore xam ple the wto pre ach edt hat the reg ula tio nsu nde rth eus cle ana ira ctw hic hse thi ghs tan dar dsa gai nst pol lut ing gas oli ned idn ota cco mmo dat ewi thw tor ule sit jud ged tha tit was unf air for the for eig noi lco mpa nie sth atp rod uce dco nta min ate doi las are sul tth eus gov ern men tre wro tet her egu lat ion sso tha tau tom obi lec ang ive off pol lut ing exh aus tan oth erw tor uli ngt hat pro duc edh arm tot hee nvi ron men tis the mar ine mam mal pro tec tio nac tsp eci fic all yth epr ovi sio nth atp rot ect sdo lph ins fro mbe ing sla ugh ter edb ytu naf ish erm anw asf oun ddi sag ree abl eul tim ate lyt hes eau tho riz edr ule swi lld ete rmi new het her the uni ted sta tes can pre ven tgr eat lak ewa ter fro mbe ing sol dto the hig hes tbi dde ror whe the rna tio nsc anr eje cti mpo rte dsh rim pca ugh tin net sth atc atc han ddr own end ang ere dse atu rtl esv een gro ota ndn ijk amp soo nwe can exp ect cha lle nge sag ain sta mer ica nla wsc ont rol lin gpe sti cid eus epr ote cti ngc omm uni tyw ate rri ght san dba nni ngr awl oge xpo rts whi chs ave sbo thf ore sts and pro ces sin gjo bsn oto nly are the ser uli ngm ade upo nth eun ite dst ate sbu tal soi not her cou ntr ies wor ldw ide inj apa nth ewt oru led aga ins tth emf orr efu sin gim por tso ffr uit pro duc tst hat car ryd ang ero usi nva siv esp eci est hus bec aus eof the seh ars hru lin gsm ade byt hew too nse ver ale nvi ron men tal act sma nyn ati ons are now fri ght ene dto con tra dic tth eco rpo rat ion sby not pro pos ing any mor ehe alt hla wsa gai nst the sec orp ora tio nst hee nvi ron men tco uld get wor sey ear byy ear thi sal sog ave adv ant age sto the cor por ati ons sin cet his hel pth eme sca pef rom dem ocr ati cla wst hat reg ula tet hei rac tiv iti est her ise inw orl dwi det rad ean dth ein cre asi ngi nte rac tio nbe twe enc oun tri esp rev iou sly sep ara ted byt rad eba rri ers hav est imu lat eda sig nif ica nti ncr eas ein tra nsp ort ati onp rog res ses ata llg eog rap hic all eve lst his has cau sed awi dev ari ety oft hre ats tot hee nvi ron men tth usa dem and ing pro ble mof glo bal iza tio nis for med bye nvi ron men tal dec ayc aus edb yth eri sei nin ter nat ion alt ran spo rta tio nth eri sei nin ter nat ion alt ran spo rta tio nco uld bep art lyb lam edo nth etr ans por tof glo bal ize dfo oda smo reg lob alc orp ora tio nst ake ove rmo sto fth eas pec tso ffa rmi ngl oca lre sou rce san dla bor sof sma llf arm ers are dec rea sin gly van ish ing thi sca use dth epe opl eto buy and eat foo dth ata reg row nov ers eas ins tea dof the loc ala rea sth usc aus ing and enc our agi ngt hea mou nto fin ter nat ion alt ran spo rta tio nth etr ans por tdi vis ion isa sig nif ica ntc ont rib uto rto loc ala irp oll uti onn ois ean noy anc ein tru sio nto lan dsc ape sco nge sti ona ndh igh fat ali tyr ate str ans por tal sod ama ges the glo bal env iro nme nti tis con tri but ing tot wom ain glo bal env iro nme nta lpr obl ems whi cha ret heg ree nho use eff ect and the dep let ion oft heo zon ela yer eve nth oug hth eef fec tso fgl oba liz ati onc ont rib ute dto man yen vir onm ent ald efe cts som ema yar gue tha tfr eet rad ewi lla voi dth eef fic ien cyl oss esa sso cia ted wit hpr ote cti oni twi llr ein for cee con omi eso fpr ogr ess ion and ent rep ren eur sar epr ovi ded wit han ins pir ati ont ose ekn eww ays toe xpo rto rco mpe tew ith imp ort sas itu ati ont hat off ers mor eop por tun iti esf orl ear nin gan din nov ati ont hei rbe lie fis tha ttr ade lib era liz ati onw ill lik ely hav eap osi tiv eef fec ton the env iro nme ntb yma kin gth eco ntr ibu tio nof res our ces mor eef fic ien tpr omo tin gec ono mic gro wth and inc rea sin gge ner alw elf are man der and cav ana gha the rea ret wom ain arg ume nts tha tar ede bat eda mon gfr eet rad esu ppo rte rsa ndt hee nvi ron men tal ist sfi rst fre etr ade rsb eli eve tha tec ono mic gro wth wil lge ner ate mor eop por tun iti esf ore nvi ron men tal pro tec tio nwh ere ase nvi ron men tal ist sfo cus ont hei ncr eas ing env iro nme nta lbu rde nca use dby eco nom icg row ths eco ndi nre lie vin gth een vir onm ent ale ffe cts oft rad een vir onm ent ali sts foc uso ntr ade pol icy whi lef ree tra der ste ndt ofo cus one nvi ron men tal pol icy cas est udi esa ren ece ssa ryt oid ent ify the lik ely eff ect sof tra del ibe ral ism for par tic ula rpr odu cts and toi nve sti gat ewh eth ero rno tth isd eve lop men tis fav ora ble for the env iro nme ntf rom ana nal ysi sof tra del ibe ral iza tio nof the coa lan dfo ods ect ort rad eli ber ali zat ion may not onl yge ner ate lar geg lob ali nco meg ain sbu tma yal sol ike lyr edu ceg lob ale nvi ron men tal dam age fro mco alc ons ump tio nan dfa rmi ngt hus fro maw elf are eco nom icv iew poi nta nds een fro maw orl dtr ade per spe cti veg lob ali zat ion sho uld enh anc eec ono mic eff ici enc ybu tth ere isc ons ide rab lyl ess con sen sus amo nge col ogi cal eco nom ics res ear che rso nwh att his mea nsi npr act ice oro nth eso cia lco sts orb ene fit sof glo bal iza tio nfo rso cie tya tla rge cha nge sin int ern ati ona ltr ade pat ter nsm ark ets tec hno log ies and com mun ica tio npa tte rns aff ect bot hth eec ono mya ndt hee nvi ron men tan der son and bla ckh urs tgl oba liz ati onh asb een spr ead wor ldw ide eve rsi nce the age ofi ndu str ial rev olu tio nit has pro ved toc rea tea cou ntr yth ati smo rei nde pen den tan dwe alt hyw ith the adv ant age off ree tra dea ndv ast rig hts fro mth ewt oho wev eri fec ono mic alg row thi sal lth epe opl eth ink abo utw hat wil lha ppe nto the env iro nme nta rou ndu sit wil lde cay int ode ple tio ndi sea ses and hea lth pro ble msd uet oth ere gul ati ons ofc ert ain act swi llb eco mea cri tic ali ssu ein the fut ure the con tin uat ion oft hee nvi ron men tal lyh aza rdo usl aws mad eby the wto wil lso med ayl ead tot het ota lde str uct ion ofn atu rea llo urn atu ral res our ces may beu sed upi fwe don otr egu lat eth efr equ ent and inc rea sin gly lar gea mou ntw eha veu sed sof art her egu lat ion ofc orp ora tee xce sse smu stb een for ced and thi swi lln otb eac hie ved thr oug hth ewt oun les sso meo nes tan dsu pan dop pos eth eru lin gsm ade byt hem the peo ple tha tsp rea dan dsu ppo rtg lob ali zat ion wil lbe the one sth atw ill bei nre mor sei fth epe opl ewh oar eaf fec ted byi tth emo std ono tfi ght for itt hen noo new ill att hee ndt hey wil lbe the one ssu ffe rin gbr brb bib lio gra phy bbr bra nde rso nka ndr bla ckh urs tth egr een ing ofw orl dtr ade iss ues new yor kha rve ste rwh eat she afm ark use njr and jrm elv int het heo ryo fin ter nat ion alt rad ene wyo rkh arp err owk rug man pra ndm itc hob stf eld eco nom icg lob ali zat ion and the env iro nme ntn ewy ork har per col lin sit sno twt oor ant iwt obu tca pit ali smo rno cap ita lis mch all eng ema nde rje rry and joh nca van agh wto fee dsc orp ora teg ree dus ato day dec asw een eyj ohn jgl oba lec ono myb eyo ndt hew ton ova flc iod ecv anp utt enm ark the env iro nme ntt rad ean dde moc rac yin ter nat ion alw ild lif eno vde cve eng roo tda nil leb van and pet ern ijk amp glo bal iza tio ntr ans por tan dth een vir onm ent new per spe cti vef ore col ogi cal eco nom ics eco log ica lec ono mic sde cbr brw ord s one oft hem ost uni que thi ngs abo utt hep lay ham let wit hha mle tpl ayi ngt hem ain cha rac ter ist hew ayr ela tio nsh ips bet wee nth ema ina ndl ess erc har act ers hav eno tch ang edf rom sha kes pea res tim epe rio din whi chh ewr ote thi spl ayt oth emo der ndi lem mas oft oda yth ech ara cte rha mle tre lat est hro ugh ind ivi dua lis mof sel fto oth ers int hep lay and sha kes pea reu ses thi sco nfu sio nof sel fan dna tur eth usa ssu rin gma nyt ype sof rea der swh oca nre lat eto his ham let cha rac ter iza tio nha mle tpo rtr ays him sel fwi tha llh ish uma nfl aws but iti sth ish uma nit yth atm ake shi mdi sti nct ive fro mev ery one els ein the sto ryi nad dit ion all ofh aml ets wak ing hou rsa rep reo ccu pie dwi thh iso wnt hou ght sth usa ddi ngm ore int ens ity toh isf eel ing san dpe rce pti ons abo utw her ehe see sim per fec tio nsw orr yan dte nsi ona swe lla sco nfu sio nbu twi tho uta dou bti tis the seh uma nqu ali tie swh ich mak esh iss itu ati ons oim pos sib lef orh imt ore sol vee asi lya not her tra gic rol eof the pla yis its iro nyt hei ron yal low sth est ory lin eto sho whu mor asw ell ast hec aus ean def fec tso fea cha cti ont ake nth ere isu sua lly lit atp lay ama jor par tin the pla yan dth ere lat ion shi psb etw een ham let and the two peo ple who hav ebe enc los est toh imb ein gop hel iaa ndt heg hos tha mle tca nno tsh are his str ong fee lin gsa nde mot ion swi thh ism oth ero rhi sgi rlf rie nda ndw hil ehi smo the ris lit era lly sle epi ngw ith the ene myo phe lia has cho sen the sid eof cla udi usb eca use ofh erf ath erp olo niu sit flo vem ake upm ysu mac tvs cen eth egh ost pro vid esh aml etw ith adi lem mai nsh ake spe are spl ays sup ern atu ral cha rac ter sar eno tal way sto bet rus ted thi nko fth eth ree wit che sin mac num ero usd eat hsb ypo iso ncl aud ius mur der edh aml ets fat her wit hpo iso nin the fin ala ctt heq uee nis the fir stt obe poi son edb ydr ink ing fro mha mle tsc upa ndt hen the poi son edt ipo him sel fha mle tsf igh twi thl aer tes ino phe lia sgr ave and the sub seq uen tdu elw oul dbo the asi lyc las sif yas man ver sus man con fli ctm ana lso str ugg les wit hna tur ein thi spl aym ost the tim eco mes for him tot ake act ion hec ann otb eca use oft his urg eto bel iev ehi sca pac ity for thi nki ngb eco mes aha ndi cap rat her tha nan adv ant age and thi sis not eve nth emo stp ain ngh imt oac ton thi sin for mat ion ist oom uch for him ham let ish owe ver ama nof dec isi onb uth eis als oco nte mpl ati veh ene eds tot hin kin ord ert oju sti fyh isa cti ons and his int ell ect rhe als oin sti gat est hef ina lac tio nth epo iso nin gof the bla des and the cup ana cti ont hat wil lba ckf ire and cau seh iso wnd eat hin the pla yth ere see mst obe aco nst ant shi fto fac tio idi ngo nly inh isb est fri end and eve nke epi ngt het rut hfr omh ism oth eru nti lth een dof act iii and the sec har act ers mig htn oth ave com eto kil lin gcl aud ius ham let doe sno tse emt odo let res emb les are alp ers onm ore tha nan yot her cha rac ter int hep lay whi chm igh tbe ano the rre aso nwh yhe sti llr ema ins asu bje cto fdi scu ssi ona ndw hyt hep lay rem ain sso pop ula rha orh ima ndg uil den ste rna ndr ose ncr ant zar eno lon ger his fri end sal soh eis awa ret hat hew ill hav eto dis gui seh ims elf and his rea lmo tiv esa ndg oal sin ord ert oat tai nth ema ndt his gpr inc ewh osf ath err ece ntl ydi edh aml ets unc lec lau diu sma rri esh ism oth ert heq uee nan dta kes the thr one ast hep lay ist old ham let fin dso uth isf ath erw asm urd ere dby the rec ent uad ius fro mbe hin dth ism ask the ygi vet hei mpr ess ion ofa per son who iss inc ere and gen uin ein rea lit yth eya rep lag ued wit hli esa nde vil the rea ppe ara nce wil lma kei tve ryd iff icu ltf orh aml ett oun cov ert het rut hth ech ara cte rsh ide beh ind pol oni ust hek ing sro yal ass ist ant has apr eoc cup ati onw ith app ear anc ehe alw ays wan tst oke epu pth eap pea ran ceo flo hol low and wit hou tfe eli ngp olo niu sgi ves his adv ice onl yto app ear tob eth elo vin gca rin gfa the rth ere ali tyi she onl ysp eak sto app ear sin cer eas apo lit ici ant olo okg ood rat her the nac tua lly beg ood and bor row ing dul lst hee dge ofh usb and ryt his abo vea llt oth ine own sel fbe tru ean dit mus tfo llo was the nig htt hed ayt hou can stn ott hen bef als eto any man far heg ive sth eap pea ran ceo fac onf ide ntf ath erw hot rus tsh iss ont ogo off onh iso wni nre ali tyh eli esa bou thi str ust for his son bys end ing asp yto wat chh imh isa dvi ceh egi ves his son
